{
  "texts": [
    "Importantly, participants were not aware that any reappraisals were produced by GPT.",
    "Each participant completed 50 trials of ratings, interspersed with four attention checks.",
    "Vignette emotion intensity & valence.",
    "Participants in both the reappraisal generation and the reappraisal rating tasks rated the emotion intensity and valence of each of the vignettes prior to conducting reappraisals.",
    "Participants rated each of the six emotions (happiness, amusement, enthusiasm, sadness, anger, anxiety) on 5-point scales of from \"none at all\" (0) to \"very much so\" (4)."
  ]
}